00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:18,640
certainly

294
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,760
These are the clothes I just bought for you

295
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:22,200
I don't want it

296
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,240
Please accept it

297
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,120
I hope you've really fixed yourself

298
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,040
certainly

299
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:28,440
Come on, I'll take you out to eat delicious food

300
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,280
No need to eat

301
00:14:30,520 --> 00:14:31,880
Don't do this again in the future

302
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:32,880
If I do it again

303
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,440
I'll really ignore you

304
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:37,200
Xiao Yun

305
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,120
Xiao Yun

306
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,400
Come and eat quickly.

307
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,880
You didn't even dry your hair.

308
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:45,800
You'll catch a cold later.

309
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:46,400
Come here.

310
00:14:49,520 --> 00:14:50,000
I...

311
00:14:51,280 --> 00:14:53,000
I have something I would like to tell you.

312
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:56,120
But I don't know how to start talking.

313
00:14:57,640 --> 00:14:58,560
My daughter.

314
00:14:58,720 --> 00:14:59,600
The words are on the tip of your tongue.

315
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:00,680
What can't you say?

316
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,400
Say it quickly.

317
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,280
Lu Yang...

318
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:05,880
He's causing trouble again.

319
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:07,480
What's up?

320
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,240
He owes a loan.

321
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,240
The loan company said,

322
00:15:11,800 --> 00:15:13,640
If he doesn't pay the debt, they will gouge out his eyes.

323
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,280
How much is the debt?

324
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:20,640
Hundreds of thousands.

325
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,360
Hundreds of thousands?

326
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:23,920
Are you kidding?

327
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,840
But he told me,

328
00:15:26,360 --> 00:15:27,200
He was very honest.

329
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:28,120
promise me

330
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:29,560
He wouldn't borrow again.

331
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:30,520
And he said

332
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,960
He's going to treat me well for the rest of his life.

333
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:36,680
Good

334
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,480
Don't be afraid

335
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:39,960
I'll deal with it

336
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:42,800
As long as it's in your best interest

337
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:44,680
I will not stand idly by

338
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,240
Thank you, uncle and aunt

339
00:16:07,760 --> 00:16:08,920
Don't cause me trouble

340
00:16:09,640 --> 00:16:12,000
I don't want to deal with the police

341
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:13,920
I will solve it
